derivation: from a compound of G5056 (τελεσφορέω) and G5342 (τελεσφορέω);
strongs_def: to be a bearer to completion (maturity), i.e. to ripen fruit (figuratively)
outline:
1. to bring to (perfection or) maturity
    1. of fruits
    2. of pregnant women
    3. of animals bringing their young to maturity
